AttributeSet.Name: App-Resources
AttributeSet.Description: Stores resources like translations for an app

Value.Value:
The brand new News App contains an amazing set of features, incl.

  1. 4 Different pre-built configurable list-views
  2. Easy to customize templates using Razor
  3. Multi-language - and EN / DE resources are already included
  4. SEO optimized templates and details URLs
  5. Support for Categories and Paging
  6. App Settings for primary location of details page - which can differ in each language
  7. Automatic thumbnailer
  8. Very-Rich inner content allows you to add apps inside posts
  9. Templates use flex-layouts and are bootstrap3 ready with SASS variables

To get started, just add it to the news page. The details-page as well as category-filter page just work automatically. 

If you want to show a short-list of news-items on another page, you will want to configure that extract to point the links to the main list - which you can do in the app settings. 

 

Test content

2sic just introduced a brand new app which is optimized for news use-cases. It's simple and includes various bootstrap3 layous - perfect for your common news requirement.

It should replace previous news and also supports Very-Rich-Content. This allows you to add galleries and more inside the news app without having to create pages for this common requirement.
